---
// Dr. Elizabeth Alejandrez - Central Dentist
import TeamMemberTemplate from '../../layouts/TeamMemberTemplate.astro';
import BlurFade from '../../components/ui/BlurFade.astro';
---

<TeamMemberTemplate
  title="Dr. Elizabeth Alejandrez | Biological Family Dentist | Central Dentist"
  description="Meet Dr. Elizabeth Alejandrez, DMD - Biological and family dentist specializing in comprehensive care, Invisalign, airway-focused health, and whole-body wellness in Dallas, TX."
  memberName="Dr. Elizabeth Alejandrez, DMD"
  role="Biological & Family Dentist"
  imageUrl="/images/team/dr-alejandrez.jpg"
  breadcrumbs={[
    { label: 'Team', href: '/team' },
    { label: 'Dr. Elizabeth Alejandrez', href: '/team/dr-elizabeth-alejandrez' }
  ]}
>
  <div slot="biography" class="bio-content">
    <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 400; color: #006786; margin-bottom: 1rem;">About Dr. Alejandrez</h3>
    <p>Dr. Elizabeth Alejandrez is dedicated to helping others improve their quality of life through biological dentistry. Her unique background in psychology and psychiatric rehabilitation, combined with her intuitive nature and curiosity, led her to expand her knowledge into biological dentistry to better serve her patients.</p>

    <p>Dr. Alejandrez's collective experiences have shaped her into a considerate and compassionate dentist who centers her practice around creating a positive experience for her patients. She combines her psychology background with dental expertise to understand the whole person, not just their oral health.</p>

    <p>She is focused on providing comprehensive care that addresses oral health and the whole body in an authentic and comfortable environment, making each patient feel heard and understood.</p>
  </div>

  <div slot="education" class="member-section bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mt-8">
    <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: #2d3748; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Education & Training</h3>
    <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">•</span>
        <span><strong>B.A. in Psychology</strong> - University of Massachusetts Lowell</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">•</span>
        <span><strong>Doctor of Medicine in Dentistry (DMD)</strong> - Tufts University School of Dental Medicine</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">•</span>
        <span><strong>Health & Wellness Coordinator</strong> - Psychiatric Rehabilitation (Prior to dental school)</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">•</span>
        <span><strong>Service Trips</strong> - Multiple international service trips during dental school</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">•</span>
        <span><strong>Invisalign Certified Provider</strong> - Advanced orthodontic training</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">•</span>
        <span><strong>Nitrous Certification</strong> - For enhanced patient comfort</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div slot="specialties" class="member-section mt-8">
    <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: #2d3748; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Clinical Expertise</h3>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #0099ba;">Comprehensive Care</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Complete diagnosis and treatment planning for all ages</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #0099ba;">Restorative Dentistry</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Biocompatible materials for function and aesthetics</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #0099ba;">Pediatric Dentistry</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Gentle care creating positive lifetime experiences</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #0099ba;">Invisalign Treatment</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Airway-focused orthodontics for optimal health</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #0099ba;">Airway Health</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Sleep-disordered breathing evaluation and treatment</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #0099ba;">Biological Dentistry</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Whole-body approach to oral health</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div slot="philosophy" class="member-section bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-6 mt-8">
    <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: #2d3748; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Personal Touch</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Outside of the clinic, Dr. Alejandrez enjoys traveling, challenging hikes, and having adventures with her husband and step-daughters. She loves playing sports and is currently embracing the discipline of tennis because, like dentistry, it is a constant and beautiful balance of learning, growth, and having fun!</p>

    <blockquote class="border-l-4 pl-6 my-6" style="border-color: #a6b443;">
      <p class="italic text-gray-700 mb-2">"I believe that oral health is a window to overall wellness. By taking a biological approach and considering the whole person, we can create lasting health improvements that go far beyond just treating teeth."</p>
      <footer class="text-sm" style="color: #0099ba;">— Dr. Elizabeth Alejandrez</footer>
    </blockquote>
  </div>

  <div slot="certifications" class="member-section bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mt-8">
    <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: #2d3748; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">Professional Affiliations</h3>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2">
      <span class="certification-badge">ADA Member</span>
      <span class="certification-badge">Texas Dental Association</span>
      <span class="certification-badge">Dallas County Dental Society</span>
      <span class="certification-badge">Invisalign Certified Provider</span>
      <span class="certification-badge">IAOMT Associate Member</span>
      <span class="certification-badge">Academy of General Dentistry</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section slot="cta" class="py-12 md:py-16" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #0099ba, #006786);">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 text-center">
      <BlurFade delay={100} client:load>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal text-white mb-4"
            style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
          Schedule a Consultation with Dr. Alejandrez
        </h2>
      </BlurFade>

      <BlurFade delay={200} client:load>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/90 mb-8" style="font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;">
          Experience compassionate biological dentistry with a focus on your complete wellness journey
        </p>
      </BlurFade>

      <BlurFade delay={300} client:load>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="px-8 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#a6b443] to-[#c7cd85] text-white rounded-full font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:from-[#8fa339] hover:to-[#a6b443] hover:shadow-lg inline-flex items-center justify-center"
            style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;"
          >
            Book Appointment
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:214-368-0900"
            class="px-8 py-3 bg-white border-2 rounded-full font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg inline-flex items-center justify-center"
            style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: #0099ba; border-color: white;"
            onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#006786'; this.style.color='white'; this.style.borderColor='#006786';"
            onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='white'; this.style.color='#0099ba'; this.style.borderColor='white';"
          >
            <svg class="mr-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
            Call Now: (214) 368-0900
          </a>
        </div>
      </BlurFade>
    </div>
  </section>

</TeamMemberTemplate>
